    <abstract>
      <t>Despite IPv6 is operational there are no protocol identifiers to 
extend the use of RMON MIBs and of the IPPM REPORTING MIB to IPv6. 
This memo defines basis protocol identifiers for IP Version 6 and  
sub IP.  
